570
00:35:11,894 --> 00:35:12,935
Please be careful.

571
00:35:14,935 --> 00:35:16,705
Someone threatened Mr. Shin with a dump truck.

572
00:35:16,774 --> 00:35:17,834
We better be careful.

573
00:35:17,905 --> 00:35:20,075
- Is he all right? - I think so.

574
00:35:40,194 --> 00:35:41,194
Hello.

575
00:35:41,194 --> 00:35:43,234
Is that the truck that threatened Mr. Shin?

576
00:35:43,464 --> 00:35:45,035
Did you take care of it?

577
00:35:45,165 --> 00:35:46,205
- Yes. - Sure.

578
00:35:46,405 --> 00:35:47,705
