594
00:37:07,785 --> 00:37:08,845
Okay, let's hurry.

595
00:37:22,935 --> 00:37:24,464
I'm sorry. It's my fault.

596
00:37:24,464 --> 00:37:25,765
Darn it.

597
00:37:30,104 --> 00:37:32,274
Over there. Tail them.

598
00:37:52,665 --> 00:37:55,124
(Husband)

599
00:37:59,964 --> 00:38:01,004
Yes, Mi Kyung.

600
00:38:03,334 --> 00:38:04,435
What were you doing?

601
