607
00:38:19,885 --> 00:38:21,254
I'm sorry, Mi Kyung.

608
00:38:21,555 --> 00:38:22,754
I'm getting a call from work.

609
00:38:23,294 --> 00:38:25,354
Okay. I'll hang up.

610
00:38:25,354 --> 00:38:27,694
Also, let's hang in there.

611
00:38:28,595 --> 00:38:30,394
Once all the papers are sorted, we'll have our hands on the money.

612
00:38:31,095 --> 00:38:33,464
Then we can choose to go anywhere we want. Okay?

613
00:38:34,665 --> 00:38:35,705
Okay.

614
00:38:49,314 --> 00:38:51,484
Honey, are you done?

615
00:38:52,185 --> 00:38:53,455
Were you loud on purpose?

616
00:38:53,455 --> 00:38:56,394
No way. What else could I do? My husband called me.

617
00:38:56,924 --> 00:38:57,924
Should I just turn it off?

618
00:39:02,635 --> 00:39:03,694
What?

619
00:39:30,155 --> 00:39:31,325
Are you okay, Mr. Shin?

620
00:39:33,665 --> 00:39:34,665
Here.

621
00:39:36,694 --> 00:39:38,694
