623
00:39:57,584 --> 00:39:58,754
(Uncle)

624
00:40:01,555 --> 00:40:03,524
Ms. Yu will have a change of heart now.

625
00:40:05,294 --> 00:40:06,524
(Uncle)

626
00:40:11,194 --> 00:40:12,435
