629
00:40:39,964 --> 00:40:42,595
I prepared a certificate of content proof worth 3.4 million.

630
00:40:43,265 --> 00:40:44,665
I still have time.

631
00:40:44,865 --> 00:40:47,004
Sure. Good luck.

632
00:40:53,745 --> 00:40:55,044
Stay here for a day,

633
00:40:55,774 --> 00:40:57,245
