634
00:40:58,314 --> 00:41:00,144
- Give me your phone. - What?

635
00:41:17,294 --> 00:41:20,504
The phone is turned off. Transferring to voicemail.

636
00:41:21,964 --> 00:41:25,635
Mr. Shin. Ms. Yu's phone is still off.

637
00:41:38,885 --> 00:41:39,924
Keep working.

638
00:41:41,624 --> 00:41:42,624
Mr. Shin.

639
00:41:44,995 --> 00:41:46,765
Where on earth did Ms. Yu go?

640
00:41:46,765 --> 00:41:49,365
She disappeared at a crucial moment.

641
00:41:49,365 --> 00:41:51,234
I think Mr. Shin will also disappear.

642
00:41:51,435 --> 00:41:52,805
He won't be able to find the money.

643
00:41:53,365 --> 00:41:54,865
That won't happen to Mr. Shin.

644
00:41:54,865 --> 00:41:57,504
How would you know? All you do is fumble around.

645
00:41:58,174 --> 00:41:59,845
Don't get sassy with me.

646
00:42:35,104 --> 00:42:38,444
The phone is turned off. Transferring to voicemail.

647
00:42:38,575 --> 00:42:41,345
You will be charged.

648
00:42:41,345 --> 00:42:42,415
(Housing Team Head Yu Mi Kyung)

649
00:42:49,024 --> 00:42:51,754
(1 Unread Message, Restricted Caller ID)

650
00:42:51,754 --> 00:42:53,564
(Seokcho Stay Peace Motel, Suite 307)

651
00:43:21,555 --> 00:43:23,095
Kang Myung Chul will soon be caught.

652
00:43:23,995 --> 00:43:26,894
He will surely pin everything on you.

653
00:43:27,595 --> 00:43:29,225
Helping us find the money...

654
00:43:29,765 --> 00:43:32,464
will taken into consideration, and you can avoid imprisonment.

655
00:43:40,845 --> 00:43:41,874
(JU Public Housing Development Project)

656
00:43:42,205 --> 00:43:44,644
Your dream is in this pamphlet...

657
00:43:45,115 --> 00:43:47,115
