658
00:43:51,785 --> 00:43:53,254
(JU Public Housing Development Project)

659
00:43:53,254 --> 00:43:55,225
For me, it was because I wanted to live a life like a fairy tale.

660
00:43:55,524 --> 00:43:57,495
To build a village and a house...

661
00:43:57,495 --> 00:43:59,095
that you'd see in a fairy tale...

662
00:43:59,924 --> 00:44:01,765
and meet a fairy-tale prince.

663
00:44:05,865 --> 00:44:07,064
The Yu Mi Kyung I remember...

664
00:44:07,604 --> 00:44:09,504
from our university days...

665
00:44:11,475 --> 00:44:13,405
was honest, dignified,

666
00:44:14,705 --> 00:44:15,944
and full of dreams.

667
00:44:21,385 --> 00:44:22,615
What happened to you?

668
00:44:34,865 --> 00:44:36,334
I found Ms. Yu.

669
00:44:37,294 --> 00:44:38,495
He found Ms. Yu.

670
00:44:38,495 --> 00:44:40,265
- Really? - I'll put you on speakerphone.

671
00:44:41,165 --> 00:44:42,905
(Manager Shin Cha Il)

672
00:44:42,905 --> 00:44:45,205
Kang Myung Chul laundered money and fabricated sources of funds...

673
00:44:45,205 --> 00:44:47,475
by purchasing and reselling construction vehicles.

674
00:44:47,644 --> 00:44:49,714
We must find his office and secure his business license,

675
00:44:49,714 --> 00:44:52,515
sales contract, and distribution contract as evidence.

676
00:44:53,314 --> 00:44:54,714
The company name is MA Distribution.

677
00:44:54,714 --> 00:44:56,144
The address is Unit 301, Naseok Building,

678
00:44:56,144 --> 00:44:57,584
20 Dongseo-gu.

679
00:44:57,785 --> 00:44:59,415
What a daring man.

680
00:44:59,415 --> 00:45:01,354
Everyone used their company.

681
00:45:01,484 --> 00:45:04,624
It's a great relief that Ms. Yu had a change of heart.

682
00:45:04,624 --> 00:45:05,955
How can you believe her?

683
00:45:06,155 --> 00:45:07,495
She's a habitual liar.

684
00:45:07,624 --> 00:45:10,595
Until we secure the evidence, I won't report her to the police.

685
00:45:10,935 --> 00:45:12,464
If she's lying, we'll turn a blind eye...

686
00:45:12,665 --> 00:45:14,004
and move on to our next plan.

687
00:45:14,834 --> 00:45:15,905
What about the money?

688
00:45:16,064 --> 00:45:17,935
She only knew Kang Myung Chul had it...

689
00:45:18,104 --> 00:45:20,075
