702
00:45:49,975 --> 00:45:52,135
Yu Mi Kyung will find out soon. She'll come clean about it all.

703
00:45:55,805 --> 00:45:56,874
That's why...

704
00:45:57,774 --> 00:45:59,615
we must find the money as soon as possible.

705
00:45:59,984 --> 00:46:01,015
Got it?

706
00:46:02,185 --> 00:46:03,385
I'll call you back.

707
00:46:16,794 --> 00:46:17,834
Let's go.

708
00:46:23,435 --> 00:46:24,475
Aren't you getting off?

709
00:46:24,935 --> 00:46:26,174
I'm not sure about stealing documents...

710
00:46:26,174 --> 00:46:27,774
from someone else's company.

711
00:46:29,475 --> 00:46:30,644
Well...

712
00:46:31,475 --> 00:46:33,685
You see, people who pocket money...

713
00:46:33,944 --> 00:46:35,285
use trust.

714
00:46:35,685 --> 00:46:38,185
This is the least we can do to catch them, no?

715
00:46:40,924 --> 00:46:42,655
I went to the elder's house yesterday.

716
00:46:43,624 --> 00:46:44,655
And...

717
00:46:45,124 --> 00:46:48,225
Min Seok and Min Hee were cooking food for him.

718
00:46:49,865 --> 00:46:51,265
Is he that unwell?

719
00:46:51,495 --> 00:46:53,805
He'll get better once we settle this problem.

720
00:46:53,805 --> 00:46:54,805
So...

721
00:46:55,234 --> 00:46:56,575
Hang in there, okay?

722
00:47:02,805 --> 00:47:04,374
- Let's go. - Okay.

723
00:47:07,785 --> 00:47:08,984
"MA Distribution."

724
00:47:10,084 --> 00:47:12,055
- It's locked. - I'll call a locksmith.

725
00:47:12,484 --> 00:47:14,225
(MA Distribution)

726
00:47:14,555 --> 00:47:15,584
Hold on.

727
00:47:21,365 --> 00:47:24,064
The window is half open. I'll climb over.

728
00:47:24,995 --> 00:47:26,705
That's too dangerous. Stop being...

729
00:47:26,905 --> 00:47:28,604
A locksmith won't open the door for you.

730
00:47:28,665 --> 00:47:29,705
I'll use the window.

731
00:47:30,004 --> 00:47:31,035
Are you serious?

732
00:47:31,405 --> 00:47:33,205
What if you fall?

733
00:47:33,305 --> 00:47:34,305
I'll be fine.

734
00:47:39,475 --> 00:47:40,484
Be careful.

735
00:47:47,354 --> 00:47:48,354
Seo Jin.

736
00:47:49,424 --> 00:47:50,894
If I fall,

737
00:47:51,095 --> 00:47:52,524
call an ambulance for me.

738
00:47:52,655 --> 00:47:54,564
How can you make a joke in this situation?

739
00:47:54,564 --> 00:47:55,725
I'm not joking.

740
00:47:56,225 --> 00:47:59,665
When the ambulance comes, ask them to open Unit 301. Got it?

741
00:47:59,865 --> 00:48:01,165
Focus, will you?

742
00:48:02,564 --> 00:48:03,604
Is it open?

743
00:48:03,805 --> 00:48:04,834
