747
00:48:24,725 --> 00:48:26,794
- Hurry up and find the documents. - All right.

748
00:48:27,595 --> 00:48:28,694
Search that side.

749
00:48:44,544 --> 00:48:45,975
(Parking Lot)

750
00:49:00,964 --> 00:49:02,095
Hold on.

751
00:49:09,305 --> 00:49:10,535
Look through these with me.

752
00:49:26,385 --> 00:49:27,484
(Car Transfer Certificate)

753
00:49:28,524 --> 00:49:30,095
(For Transferor and Transferee's Direct Transaction)

754
00:49:30,354 --> 00:49:31,555
I might've found it.

755
00:49:32,325 --> 00:49:33,365
(Business Registration Certificate)

756
00:49:33,365 --> 00:49:35,124
- It's these, right? - I think so.

757
00:49:45,475 --> 00:49:46,905
(MA Distribution)

758
00:50:04,225 --> 00:50:05,995
Can you call the insurance company?

759
00:50:06,155 --> 00:50:07,464
