770
00:50:51,334 --> 00:50:52,535
Seriously.

771
00:50:55,504 --> 00:50:56,714
Are you okay, Han Soo?

772
00:50:56,714 --> 00:50:58,144
We must catch Kang Myung Chul.

773
00:51:00,115 --> 00:51:01,115
Darn it.

774
00:51:10,194 --> 00:51:11,254
Hurry, Seo Jin!

775
00:51:20,905 --> 00:51:22,205
I'm sorry, Mr. Shin.

776
00:51:22,365 --> 00:51:24,604
Kang Myung Chul took the documents. We're chasing after him.

777
00:51:24,935 --> 00:51:27,274
He must be heading to where he hid the money.

778
00:51:27,504 --> 00:51:28,575
Don't lose him.

779
00:51:28,575 --> 00:51:29,705
Understood.

780
00:51:48,095 --> 00:51:49,694
Where could he have gone?

781
00:51:55,334 --> 00:51:56,535
Don't you remember this road?

782
00:51:57,305 --> 00:51:58,874
We took this road when tailing Ms. Lee Yeon Ji.

783
00:52:20,265 --> 00:52:21,265
Over there.

784
00:52:31,935 --> 00:52:33,305
He must've taken it already.

785
00:52:44,984 --> 00:52:46,285
Mr. Kang.

786
00:52:46,515 --> 00:52:48,084
- Return the money. - Hey.

787
00:52:48,084 --> 00:52:49,424
Let go while I ask nicely.

788
00:52:49,424 --> 00:52:50,955
- I can't. - You can't?

789
00:52:52,024 --> 00:52:53,155
Let go.

790
00:52:54,325 --> 00:52:57,365
Why won't you listen to me?

791
00:53:01,705 --> 00:53:02,865
Is this the police?

792
00:53:03,035 --> 00:53:04,305
I'm at...

793
00:53:04,305 --> 00:53:06,535
I'm at Angu-ro 23. Get over here fast.

794
00:53:06,535 --> 00:53:08,345
- Return the money. - Let go of me.

795
00:53:08,705 --> 00:53:09,805
Let go, punk!

796
00:53:10,374 --> 00:53:13,314
Why don't you do as you're told? You're like a leech.

797
00:54:10,274 --> 00:54:11,305
Hey.

798
00:54:11,305 --> 00:54:12,975
I'm sick and tired of you all.

799
00:54:14,274 --> 00:54:15,444
You deserve a beating.

800
00:54:25,385 --> 00:54:26,385
My gosh.

801
00:54:26,385 --> 00:54:28,084
Why do you bring this upon yourself?

802
00:54:28,084 --> 00:54:29,155
Mr. Shin!

803
00:54:30,995 --> 00:54:32,055
Darn you.

804
00:54:33,325 --> 00:54:34,725
You're begging for a beating.

805
00:54:34,964 --> 00:54:36,265
