806
00:54:41,165 --> 00:54:43,104
Why do you never give up?

807
00:54:43,365 --> 00:54:44,705
Do what you will,

808
00:54:44,705 --> 00:54:46,604
but you're nothing but your boss' hound.

809
00:54:47,345 --> 00:54:48,504
Darn it.

810
00:55:13,035 --> 00:55:14,334
Shoot.

811
00:55:23,674 --> 00:55:24,745
Hey.

812
00:55:24,774 --> 00:55:25,915
It was a trick.

813
00:55:28,015 --> 00:55:29,845
The money's not here.

814
00:55:31,354 --> 00:55:32,615
You and I both...

815
00:55:32,714 --> 00:55:34,655
were tricked. Darn it.

816
00:55:45,136 --> 00:55:48,507
Finnair has a boarding announcement.

817
00:55:49,136 --> 00:55:52,806
Finnair flight 1207 set to depart at 19:50...

818
00:55:53,246 --> 00:55:56,647
will begin boarding in Section F. Please use boarding gate three.

819
00:56:23,007 --> 00:56:24,476
(Long-term Airport Parking E5)

820
00:56:30,686 --> 00:56:31,786
We found it.

821
00:56:32,346 --> 00:56:33,487
Open it up.

822
00:56:57,007 --> 00:56:58,306
I was right, wasn't I?

823
00:56:58,346 --> 00:57:00,277
People rarely change.

824
00:57:01,317 --> 00:57:04,116
They tried so hard to be smart. What a shame.

825
00:57:04,147 --> 00:57:06,917
I think it was stupid of them to hide it in the car trunk.

826
00:57:06,917 --> 00:57:07,956
Right?

827
00:57:08,156 --> 00:57:11,087
They thought no one would notice a car in the long-stay parking lot.

828
00:57:11,786 --> 00:57:13,726
That complacent mindset...

829
00:57:13,826 --> 00:57:15,427
is why they got caught.

830
00:57:18,027 --> 00:57:20,067
Han Soo Gu. What are you reading?

831
00:57:20,536 --> 00:57:22,366
Will you leave him alone?

832
00:57:22,366 --> 00:57:24,107
I'll make you a coffee.

833
00:57:25,406 --> 00:57:26,906
(JU Public Housing Development Project)

834
00:57:26,906 --> 00:57:28,306
(A fairy-tale house in a fairy-tale village)

835
00:57:35,746 --> 00:57:38,947
We recovered three million dollars taken from the development project.

836
00:57:39,917 --> 00:57:41,087
We'll seize Kang Myung Chul...

837
00:57:41,217 --> 00:57:43,556
and Yu Mi Kyung's assets to recover the rest.

838
00:57:45,156 --> 00:57:47,226
Why are you causing me so much trouble?

839
00:57:49,197 --> 00:57:50,467
I never did.

840
00:57:51,467 --> 00:57:52,627
Leave.

841
00:58:06,076 --> 00:58:07,746
Darn it.

842
00:58:09,016 --> 00:58:11,447
(Vice President Hwang Dae Woong)

843
00:58:13,386 --> 00:58:15,757
Oh, my gosh...

844
00:58:23,427 --> 00:58:24,596
This is Shin Cha Il.

845
00:58:31,067 --> 00:58:32,266
Very well.

846
00:58:34,877 --> 00:58:36,036
Good job.

847
00:58:36,476 --> 00:58:37,547
Did you get the text?

848
00:58:40,777 --> 00:58:42,447
(1 Unread Message, Restricted Caller ID)

849
00:58:42,447 --> 00:58:43,817
(Seokcho Stay Peace Motel, Suite 307)

850
00:58:45,116 --> 00:58:46,217
I hope you understand.

851
00:58:46,217 --> 00:58:48,016
Dae Woong gave me no choice.

852
00:58:49,857 --> 00:58:52,587
Mr. Shin, what do you think of the Vice President Hwang?

853
00:58:52,786 --> 00:58:54,797
Do you think JU Construction needs him?

854
00:59:04,536 --> 00:59:05,636
Sir.

855
00:59:06,406 --> 00:59:08,806
Can I tell the union members we recovered their money?

856
00:59:11,007 --> 00:59:13,076
How about we go together to tell...

857
00:59:13,076 --> 00:59:14,177
You go ahead.

858
00:59:14,877 --> 00:59:16,746
Yes, sir. Got it.

859
00:59:28,527 --> 00:59:30,127
(Let's go to my parents' place after work.)

860
00:59:35,337 --> 00:59:37,306
Let's go to my parents' place after work.

861
00:59:37,607 --> 00:59:39,967
The kids will come with their grandfather.

862
00:59:42,306 --> 00:59:44,806
I have something to do. You can go.

863
00:59:46,047 --> 00:59:48,246
Min Hee and Min Seok will want to see you.

864
01:00:00,087 --> 01:00:01,697
I didn't think you'd come.

865
01:00:02,297 --> 01:00:03,697
I heard you wanted to say something.

866
01:00:07,127 --> 01:00:08,936
You came straight to the airport.

867
01:00:10,936 --> 01:00:13,266
That means you didn't trust me completely.

868
01:00:16,636 --> 01:00:18,206
I wanted revenge.

869
01:00:20,406 --> 01:00:21,777
To get back at him.

870
01:00:22,576 --> 01:00:23,877
That's why I did it.

871
01:00:25,317 --> 01:00:26,346
I'm sorry.

872
01:00:26,346 --> 01:00:27,956
Once the trial begins,

873
01:00:28,556 --> 01:00:30,886
I'll testify in detail about how...

874
01:00:31,456 --> 01:00:34,757
you deceived everyone and how you lied to your staff.

875
01:00:35,456 --> 01:00:39,027
I'll show there's no mercy for an embezzler.

876
01:00:42,667 --> 01:00:44,766
You've changed so much.

877
01:00:45,837 --> 01:00:46,967
Do you know that?

878
01:00:47,576 --> 01:00:49,737
I didn't know I'd changed...

879
01:00:50,306 --> 01:00:51,877
until I saw you again.

880
01:00:53,107 --> 01:00:54,476
You don't know...

881
01:00:54,817 --> 01:00:56,717
how much you've changed, do you?

882
01:00:59,587 --> 01:01:00,817
I do know.

883
01:01:02,456 --> 01:01:03,757
It was a choice.

884
01:01:04,456 --> 01:01:05,627
Why?

885
01:01:06,286 --> 01:01:07,927
Why did you make that choice?

886
01:01:07,927 --> 01:01:09,627
Because of people like you.

887
01:01:13,027 --> 01:01:14,297
Forgive me.

888
01:01:16,366 --> 01:01:18,036
I dated the wrong guy.

889
01:01:19,436 --> 01:01:21,306
You said so yourself...

890
01:01:21,636 --> 01:01:23,777
that I was honest, dignified, and full of dreams.

891
01:01:23,777 --> 01:01:27,817
I'm facing Yu Mi Kyung who is locked up for embezzlement.

892
01:01:27,817 --> 01:01:28,976
Cha Il.

893
01:01:30,047 --> 01:01:32,047
I won't last in a place like this.

894
01:01:32,447 --> 01:01:33,886
You got the money back.

895
01:01:34,217 --> 01:01:35,857
Talk to the union members...

896
01:01:35,857 --> 01:01:37,156
Do you still think...

897
01:01:40,487 --> 01:01:41,927
I'm a romantic?

898
01:01:49,636 --> 01:01:52,067
I'll do my best to show everyone that it's a grave sin...

899
01:01:53,266 --> 01:01:55,177
to betray someone's trust.

900
01:02:15,496 --> 01:02:17,397
(Yes! Chicken)

901
01:02:22,436 --> 01:02:25,306
Enjoy. This is all for you.

902
01:02:25,306 --> 01:02:26,636
- Really? - Yes.

903
01:02:27,167 --> 01:02:29,036
It's not spicy, so you'll like it. Eat up.

904
01:02:29,036 --> 01:02:30,277
- Thank you. - Thank you.

905
01:02:30,277 --> 01:02:31,547
- No problem. - Thanks, Mom.

906
01:02:32,746 --> 01:02:35,746
Let's see. Here, Min Hee.

907
01:02:36,116 --> 01:02:39,047
Here, Min Seok. Eat as much as you want.

908
01:02:39,717 --> 01:02:41,987
Thank you for helping me get my money back.

909
01:02:41,987 --> 01:02:43,317
I just did my job. That's all.

910
01:02:43,317 --> 01:02:44,627
- My gosh. - I'm sorry you went through that.

911
01:02:44,757 --> 01:02:47,357
By the way, how come Seo Jin isn't here?

912
01:02:47,427 --> 01:02:50,697
Well, she had to take care of something.

913
01:02:50,697 --> 01:02:52,496
I miss her.

914
01:02:52,496 --> 01:02:53,697
You do?

915
01:02:53,697 --> 01:02:55,297
I promise you I'll bring her next time.

916
01:02:55,766 --> 01:02:57,197
But you have to eat a lot today, Min Hee.

917
01:02:57,967 --> 01:02:58,967
Here.

918
01:02:59,467 --> 01:03:01,677
- You too, sir. Have some. - Yes, all right.

919
01:03:05,246 --> 01:03:07,246
How is it, kids? Isn't it good?

920
01:03:07,547 --> 01:03:09,147
- Yes, it's yummy. - Right?

921
01:03:10,047 --> 01:03:13,016
Actually, the union rep called me earlier.

922
01:03:13,587 --> 01:03:15,357
I guess they let you make phone calls...

923
01:03:15,357 --> 01:03:16,717
in a holding cell these days?

924
01:03:16,717 --> 01:03:18,386
What did he say?

925
01:03:18,456 --> 01:03:20,587
He kept apologizing over and over.

926
01:03:21,056 --> 01:03:23,726
He said he wasn't thinking straight because he was so broke.

927
01:03:24,167 --> 01:03:25,627
He was bawling.

928
01:03:26,427 --> 01:03:27,496
So I told him...

929
01:03:28,237 --> 01:03:29,936
never to make the same mistake again.

930
01:03:31,507 --> 01:03:33,366
You forgave him?

931
01:03:33,366 --> 01:03:35,306
How are you going to live your life...

932
01:03:35,306 --> 01:03:37,476
if you hate people just because you've been scammed once?

933
01:03:37,947 --> 01:03:39,277
Life is short.

934
01:03:43,047 --> 01:03:44,076
Eat as much as you like.

935
01:04:11,476 --> 01:04:12,677
- Get going. Bye. - Good night, sir.

936
01:04:17,246 --> 01:04:18,246
Hey, kiddo.

937
01:04:18,246 --> 01:04:19,286
What are you doing here at this hour?

938
01:04:19,786 --> 01:04:21,556
I have something to tell you.

939
01:04:21,556 --> 01:04:22,656
Okay, what is it?

940
01:04:23,817 --> 01:04:24,987
I also helped the union members...

941
01:04:26,627 --> 01:04:27,697
get their money back.

942
01:04:28,897 --> 01:04:30,897
They're all struggling financially,

943
01:04:31,096 --> 01:04:32,826
and they'd be homeless without that money,

944
01:04:33,397 --> 01:04:35,496
so I thought helping them was the right thing to do.

945
01:04:36,067 --> 01:04:37,436
That's why I helped Mr. Shin.

946
01:04:39,866 --> 01:04:40,906
Good.

947
01:04:41,706 --> 01:04:43,476
Of course, you should help your manager.

948
01:04:43,476 --> 01:04:46,246
Why did you tell us not to find the money?

949
01:04:50,647 --> 01:04:51,717
Did you have dinner?

950
01:04:52,186 --> 01:04:54,487
How about I flaunt my cooking skills for you? It's been a while.

951
01:04:54,717 --> 01:04:55,817
Kimchi fried rice.

952
01:04:56,116 --> 01:04:57,587
You like kimchi fried rice.

953
01:04:58,927 --> 01:05:01,456
Sorry. Maybe another time.

954
01:05:12,667 --> 01:05:15,136
Darn it.

955
01:05:19,877 --> 01:05:20,947
- Hello. - Let's eat!

956
01:05:21,976 --> 01:05:24,147
This is nice.

957
01:05:24,417 --> 01:05:25,516
I want more.

958
01:05:28,516 --> 01:05:31,487
Mr. Shin, they gave me this at the reception.

959
01:05:31,487 --> 01:05:32,656
They said it came via express courier.

960
01:05:38,096 --> 01:05:40,197
(Manager Shin Cha Il)

961
01:05:50,576 --> 01:05:52,107
(Audit those running the construction site dining halls,)

962
01:05:52,107 --> 01:05:53,877
(or everyone who uses JU Construction's dining halls...)

963
01:05:53,877 --> 01:05:55,647
(will be hurt, including the cafeteria at the head office!)

964
01:05:55,647 --> 01:05:56,677
(The construction site for the shopping mall...)

965
01:05:56,677 --> 01:05:57,686
(is the first target!)

966
01:06:12,127 --> 01:06:13,167
- What's wrong? - Hey!

967
01:06:13,697 --> 01:06:14,737
- Oh, no. - What should we do?

968
01:06:14,737 --> 01:06:17,567
- What is going on? - Gosh, I feel sick.

969
01:06:32,587 --> 01:06:33,647
Everyone, stop eating.

970
01:06:41,956 --> 01:06:42,996
All of you!

971
01:06:44,467 --> 01:06:46,366
Stop eating.

972
01:06:48,137 --> 01:06:51,066
(The Auditors)

973
01:06:51,066 --> 01:06:53,507
(Special thanks to Hong Soo Hyun and Lee Shin Ki)

974
01:07:11,286 --> 01:07:13,557
I want you to look into it, in secret.

975
01:07:13,656 --> 01:07:15,356
What about the person who sent the threatening letter?

976
01:07:15,356 --> 01:07:16,727
We will find out.

977
01:07:16,856 --> 01:07:18,167
If they snoop around and comb through stuff,

978
01:07:18,167 --> 01:07:19,297
they'll find all sorts of things.

979
01:07:19,297 --> 01:07:20,866
Why Mr. Shin, of all people?

980
01:07:21,066 --> 01:07:23,337
You think everyone is corrupt...

981
01:07:23,337 --> 01:07:24,967
and is deceiving others, don't you?

982
01:07:24,967 --> 01:07:26,337
Has anyone asked you for a favor...

983
01:07:26,337 --> 01:07:27,837
regarding the management rights?

984
01:07:28,776 --> 01:07:29,937
Where do you think you're going?

985
01:07:29,937 --> 01:07:32,877
Bring me one solid piece of evidence!

986
01:07:33,076 --> 01:07:34,517
I'll write an official apology letter...

987
01:07:34,776 --> 01:07:37,847
and post it on every intranet forum.

988
01:07:38,246 --> 01:07:40,387
In conclusion, the audit was unreasonable.
